# --- Published extension artifacts ---------------------------------------
# Un-ignore compiled artifacts inside docs/extensions/ so GitHub Pages can
# serve them. `*.vsix` and `*.duckdb*` above would otherwise exclude the
# .vsix downloads and the .duckdb_extension.gz files the CI publish step
# commits to this tree.
!docs/extensions/**/*.vsix
!docs/extensions/**/*.duckdb_extension
!docs/extensions/**/*.duckdb_extension.gz
